  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\"><img alt=\"House Lannister.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/50px-House_Lannister.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/75px-House_Lannister.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d5/House_Lannister.svg/100px-House_Lannister.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lady</span><br />Margot Lannister</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Peake\" title=\"House Peake\"><img alt=\"House Peake.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b2/House_Peake.svg/50px-House_Peake.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b2/House_Peake.svg/75px-House_Peake.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b2/House_Peake.svg/100px-House_Peake.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\nLady of <a href=\"/index.php/Starpike\" title=\"Starpike\">Starpike</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Peake\" title=\"House Peake\">House Peake</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nLord <a href=\"/index.php/Titus_Peake\" title=\"Titus Peake\">Titus Peake</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Lady <b>Margot Lannister</b> is a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a>, a distant cousin of the main branch. She is married to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Titus_Peake\" title=\"Titus Peake\">Titus Peake</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Starpike\" title=\"Starpike\">Starpike</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Margot_Lannister&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Appendix\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Appendix\">A